{"tid":690463,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"朝鮮局勢】白宮：美朝峰會進展順利，暫定下周二早上９時會面","createTime":"2018-06-05T01:47:47.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-05T05:05:07.000Z","uid":184679,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"65ac55e57de018655afacbbd30cde7e7d2ee7292","tid":690463,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-05T01:47:47.000Z","msg":"美國白宮表示，美國總統特朗普與北韓領導人金正恩會晤的準備工作進展順利，兩人暫定於６月１２日（周二）早上９時在新加坡會面。<br />\n<br />\n三日之前特朗普在白宮接見北捍高級代表團，後者向特朗普轉交金正恩的信件。在被問及金<br />\n正恩的信函內容時，白宮發言人桑德斯僅指，美朝關係正繼續向前發展，並已取得良好進展。<br />\n<br />\n當被問及美國向北韓施加最大壓力的行動會否繼續時，桑德斯稱，美國的政策並未改變，華<br />\n府仍維持對北韓的嚴厲制裁措施，除非平壤實現無核化。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.etnet.com.hk/www/tc/news/categorized_news_detail.php?newsid=ETN280605231&amp;page=1&amp;category=latest\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.etnet.com.hk%2Fwww%2Ftc%2Fnews%2Fcategorized_news_detail.php%3Fnewsid%3DETN280605231%26page%3D1%26category%3Dlatest&d=Zt5PrfE02W2MKJ332E7kZxOFz4pMHIf1Ti9x7C0XgVU%3D&h=b0551a36\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.etnet.com.hk/www/tc/news/categorized_news_detail.php?newsid=ETN280605231&amp;page=1&amp;category=latest</a><br />\n<br />\n開波<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f030cc075da6126fac5cc53ee42f9d439f97bec5","tid":690463,"uid":34409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-05T02:06:39.000Z","msg":"要睇E3 喎"},{"pid":"ff143e0b390a34bbd99de47a9416c54e39031a95","tid":690463,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-05T03:35:02.000Z","msg":"美朝峰會個劇本就好似美國軍隊長3做做下變咗做復仇者聯盟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a0b727ebab82f9f935ceb33b4540187201f53b83","tid":690463,"uid":104699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-05T05:03:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"894ba6fca7a95a920a42c09aee0a5e27c5830265","tid":690463,"uid":44171,"like":1,"disli